<li>Houston: <a href="/wiki/KRIV_(TV)" title="KRIV (TV)">KRIV 26</a> (Astros, <i>1979–1982</i>), <a href="/wiki/KTXH" title="KTXH">KTXH 20</a> (Astros, <i>1983–1997</i>, <i>2008–2012</i>)</li>
<li>Detroit: <a href="/wiki/WJBK" title="WJBK">WJBK 2</a> (Tigers, <i>1953–1974</i>; <i>2007</i>)</li>
<li>Minneapolis–Saint Paul: <a href="/wiki/KMSP-TV" title="KMSP-TV">KMSP 9</a> (Twins, <i>1979–1988</i>, <i>1998–2002</i>), <a href="/wiki/WFTC" title="WFTC">WFTC 29</a> (Twins, <i>1990–1992</i>, <i>2005–2010</i>)</li></ul>
